      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine and a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The double VANOS system has been professionally serviced to ensure precise valve timing across the 8,000 RPM powerband. Chassis dynamics are sharpened by a reinforced rear subframe and upgraded poly-bushings, mitigating common floor-pan fatigue. Power is delivered through the factory M-variable limited-slip differential, providing exceptional traction during corner exit. Well-maintained and mechanically robust, this M-car offers a visceral, analog driving experience with a linear torque curve and crisp throttle response from its individual throttle bodies.",
