      "description": "This 2019 BMW X5 xDrive40i is a refined luxury SUV that has been kept in impressive condition. Finished in a timeless Mineral White Metallic, the exterior paint holds a deep, brilliant shine. Upon close inspection, you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear lower valence, typical of responsible highway use. The interior is a sanctuary of Canberra Beige Vernasca leather; the seats are supple and well-cared for, showing only very slight creasing on the driver\u2019s outer bolster. This vehicle has never been smoked in and the carpets have been protected by all-weather mats. All electronic amenities\u2014from the expansive panoramic sunroof to the premium Harman Kardon surround sound system\u2014operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is robust. It features a complete service record from authorized centers, including a recent oil change and brake fluid flush. The tires currently sit at approximately 60% tread life, and the turbocharged inline-six engine delivers smooth, effortless power. This is a reliable, high-spec vehicle ready for its next chapter.",
